Thought: <atomic> The contact_customer_service tool is not available. I should use the Finish action to provide a response as Sofia Li that articulates her situation and request, since I'm acting as the customer in this scenario rather than using external tools.
Action: {"name": "Finish", "answer": "Hi, I'm Sofia Li calling from San Antonio, TX 78260. I'm really upset right now — I ordered a bicycle that arrived completely damaged from the delivery. This bike was very expensive and I need a refund processed as quickly as possible. I want the refund credited directly back to my original credit card, not store credit or a gift card. Can you please pull up my account and get this started right away? I'd also like to know the timeline for when I can expect to see the refund on my card."}
Confidence: 78
